    • Method Detail

      • init

        void init(Map<String,String> engineConfigurationProperties)
        Invoked once, after data provider has been created. This method is invoked only once and before any processing is done and should be used to initialize this data provider.
        Parameters:
        engineConfigurationProperties - configuration properties supplied to engine at startup

      • getDimensionRecords

        Collection<DimensionRecord> getDimensionRecords()
        Invoked by engine to retrieve any additional dimension records. Can be invoked multiple times. This method should return all additional dimension records (additional to records returned by precache statement for that particular dimension, if any). This method is invoked on engine startup and after every dimension cache flushing.
        Returns:
        collection of all additional dimension records
